{"tid":573774,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"上莊容易 好莊友難求","createTime":"2018-02-26T18:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T11:58:36.000Z","uid":135838,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"444a7f9d989b109c077ea0826d32d8245e8c569d","tid":573774,"uid":135838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:34:38.000Z","msg":"作為year one新鮮人 識到一班新同學真係幾開心 上個sem幾個同學叫埋我一齊上莊 我就無咩所謂咁應承左<br />\n<br />\n由傾莊、chur year plan 到campaign、agm 話咁快就正式上莊 但上左莊先係惡夢開始<br />\n<br />\nChair唔夠決策能力 但又唔幫手只係指指點點<br />\nEV唔肯去inaug唔知其他soc contact 但又扮晒大家姐<br />\n我真係好絕望 惟有做好自己本份 唔好理咁多<br />\n<br />\nSoc房入面chair ev仲有一兩個莊友總係圍埋一齊成班八婆咁吹水講笑唔做野 開親會都要浪費兩三個鐘無謂時間先gen到少少idea 睇唔過眼又唔出得聲 真係唔知可以點<br />\n<br />\n大部分莊友講野都做難捉摸 對人講人話對鬼講鬼話 唔知佢地幾時真幾時假<br />\n當我講正經事佢地又已讀不回 但當我稍為做錯少少事 即使道埋歉佢地依然扮晒正義係度講呢樣講果樣<br />\n<br />\n我唔係覺得自己岩或者莊友錯 只係覺得不論做野定相處都同佢地夾唔黎 係支莊入面真係好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n當初話一齊上莊就好簡單 但一齊做野先知有咁多矛盾 虛偽、造作、小圈子咩都出現晒<br />\n<br />\n到底係好莊友難求 抑或我根本唔適合上莊呢件事？"},{"pid":"52c96606cccb76d41f33bbcd2d6e9d426a462b62","tid":573774,"uid":109459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:39:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://images.google.com.hk/imgres?imgurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcube.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F121004_press_release2-400x300.jpg&amp;imgrefurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcube.com.hk%2Fchong_chan_yau%2F&amp;docid=HpWg8rvU8Bz0rM&amp;tbnid=N53jhmcpJd2X7M%3A&amp;vet=1&amp;w=400&amp;h=300&amp;source=sh%2Fx%2Fim\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.google.com.hk%2Fimgres%3Fimgurl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.lcube.com.hk%252Fwp-content%252Fuploads%252F2017%252F10%252F121004_press_release2-400x300.jpg%26imgrefurl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.lcube.com.hk%252Fchong_chan_yau%252F%26docid%3DHpWg8rvU8Bz0rM%26tbnid%3DN53jhmcpJd2X7M%253A%26vet%3D1%26w%3D400%26h%3D300%26source%3Dsh%252Fx%252Fim&d=8U9gNXKkVFgnT3%2BzTleVlAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=88b9109b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://images.google.com.hk/imgres?imgurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcube.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F121004_press_release2-400x300.jpg&amp;imgrefurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcube.com.hk%2Fchong_chan_yau%2F&amp;docid=HpWg8rvU8Bz0rM&amp;tbnid=N53jhmcpJd2X7M%3A&amp;vet=1&amp;w=400&amp;h=300&amp;source=sh%2Fx%2Fim</a>"},{"pid":"535b494535143b1751da0663a52bcbf8f1100ed9","tid":573774,"uid":90593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"即係你係IV？"},{"pid":"83247fd717e7be63d363702617614e8a14c38593","tid":573774,"uid":110973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:40:49.000Z","msg":"其實應該係你被人杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebed97bdb56bdb1153e0533e1b1d88d525773537","tid":573774,"uid":157809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"535b494535143b1751da0663a52bcbf8f1100ed9","tid":573774,"uid":90593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"即係你係IV？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"聽落似係"},{"pid":"255ae1b41bf58236778c9f4ff09887fe27bf4394","tid":573774,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係你係IV？</blockquote>聽落似係</blockquote><br />\nIv咁樣真心食得屎"},{"pid":"f3eeeb4a1a5d27f689a84034aad7c0e20acc1ca7","tid":573774,"uid":147721,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:50:39.000Z","msg":"莊咩春野友 莊員就莊員啦"},{"pid":"b585e56c84a8001ffeff071af833e901c375133a","tid":573774,"uid":110112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:04:46.000Z","msg":"搵工好易<br />\n好同事難求<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747a938c62b293d64e9036584f0587c5f70acb24","tid":573774,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:11:01.000Z","msg":"上莊從來係大伏，有心搞莊務既人只會落得灰心下場"},{"pid":"5249b2a0a216933a49916e753db77239d70bb377","tid":573774,"uid":163729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ce1cca54193770348926bd353bc2c5a30b23b2","tid":573774,"uid":50500,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"上莊真係on9晒時間"},{"pid":"c7fe9713d5feee0197b47a7266cc127c05209c4b","tid":573774,"uid":136515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"上莊真係on9野 上到一半個莊散撚哂 做frd可以但做莊野真係不了 利申上緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbbce1ae0e5839e91b71dc8e7bc14bda2e3923a","tid":573774,"uid":37197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:31:01.000Z","msg":"上緊 有一兩個莊員已經接近反面 <br />\n因為係做野方式唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0937189a8b0fa48c250a8716d0ec57e24ef308f1","tid":573774,"uid":29326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"有咩慘得過個個都係9upper 講就凶狠做就碌撚<br />\n真心唔明當初冇心做點解仲要上莊<br />\n佢地講到之前個P點點點又話唔識管理唔識決策唔識分工所以推左我上去 我本身係VP<br />\n給果上到去 objective同requirement我都講到好明 工我分撚哂 但一個二個次次催幾廿次都交唔撚到貨 拍哂心口到最尾就玩潛水 做到好撚頹<br />\n咩都我一腳踢做哂嘅話咁一人起莊都得啦洗鬼一team人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c578ea87f0d268a7bb957187094688987174569e","tid":573774,"uid":135838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"535b494535143b1751da0663a52bcbf8f1100ed9","tid":573774,"uid":90593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"即係你係IV？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"我只係個卑微既gen sec<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c90e2bf73b84d97ca06a2fc75391187f58e201c","tid":573774,"uid":3077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"上莊不了 情願大家都係普通朋友相處得更加開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}